'''Mac App Store'''是[[苹果公司|苹果公司]]开发的[[macOS|macOS]]应用程式數位发布平台。该平台于2010年10月20日在苹果的“Back to the Mac”大会中宣布。<ref name="Jan6">{{cite web |url=http://www.engadget.com/2010/12/16/apple-mac-app-store-open-for-business-starting-january-6th/ |title=Apple Mac App Store: open for business starting January 6th |author=Darren Murph |date=December 6, 2010 |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |accessdate=December 16, 2010 |archive-date=2019-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116230658/https://www.engadget.com/2010/12/16/apple-mac-app-store-open-for-business-starting-january-6th/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="1-6-10-PCMAG-MACAPPSTORE">{{cite web | url=http://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2375320,00.asp | title=Apple's Mac App Store: Hands On | accessdate=2011-01-06 | date=2011-01-06 | work=PC Magazine | publisher=PC Magazine | archive-date=2019-01-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104145616/https://www.pcmag.com/article2/0,2817,2375320,00.asp | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="appleinsider 90 days">{{cite web |url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/10/10/20/apples_new_mac_app_store_coming_to_snow_leopard_within_90_days.html |title=Apple's new Mac App Store coming to Snow Leopard within 90 days |author=AppleInsider Staff |date=20 October 2010 |work=AppleInsider.com |publisher= |accessdate=31 October 2010 |archive-date=2020-07-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200726154941/https://appleinsider.com/articles/10/10/20/apples_new_mac_app_store_coming_to_snow_leopard_within_90_days.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>苹果自2010年11月3日起开始接受已注册开发者提交的应用。<ref name="accepting app submissions">{{cite web |url=http://macappstorereview.com/2010/11/03/apple-now-accepting-submissions-for-the-mac-app-store/ |title=Apple Now Accepting Submissions For The Mac App Store |author=Mac App Store Review |date=3 November 2010 |work=MacAppStoreReview.com |publisher= |accessdate=3 November 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101109005721/http://macappstorereview.com/2010/11/03/apple-now-accepting-submissions-for-the-mac-app-store/ |archivedate=2010年11月9日 }}</ref> 

2011年1月6日，Mac App Store作为Mac OS X 10.6.6免费更新的一部分发布给所有[[Mac_OS_X_Snow_Leopard|Snow Leopard]]用户。<ref name="Jan6"/><ref name="1-6-10-PCMAG-MACAPPSTORE" />在上线24小时后，苹果宣布Mac App Store中的应用程式下载量已超过一百万次。<ref>{{cite press release |title=Mac App Store Downloads Top One Million in First Day |publisher=[[Apple_Inc.|Apple Inc.]] |date=January 7, 2011 |url=http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2011/01/07macappstore.html |accessdate=2011-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110110060115/http://www.apple.com/pr/library/2011/01/07macappstore.html |archive-date=2011-01-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 苹果公司使用情况 ==
自Mac App Store发布以来，苹果公司逐渐开始使用其作为发布自家软件产品的主要方式。这一形势在2011年发布[[OS_X_Lion|OS X Lion]]时变得更为凸出。Lion是第一个不經由[[Apple_Store|Apple Store]]销售盒装DVD这种传统方式发布的OS X版本。在Lion发布之后，苹果又提供了操作系统USB快閃磁碟機等分发方式。

[[Dashboard|Dashboard]] widget資料库和[[Safari|Safari]]擴充資料库仍然以線上网页形式存在，没有受到影响。内容可以追溯到1998年之前的技术支援下载页也被保留，主要提供较早及目前的操作系统和软件的安全更新。

== 指引 ==
类似于[[iOS|iOS]] [[App_Store_(iOS)|App Store]]，Mac App Store由苹果监管。 透过Mac App Store销售的应用程式在上架之前必须通过苹果的审核。从2012年6月1日起，所有新提交到App Store的程序必须使用沙盒，否则不能上架。此举旨在提高Mac的安全性，但也限制了一些應用程式的重要功能。<ref name="macworld details">{{cite web |url=http://www.macworld.com/article/155120/2010/10/mac_app_store_devil_in_the_details.html?lsrc=rss_main |title=The Mac App Store: The devil will be in the details |author=Dan Frakes |date=23 October 2010 |work=Macworld.com |publisher=Mac Publishing, LLC |accessdate=24 October 2010 |archive-date=2012-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304153641/http://www.macworld.com/article/155120/2010/10/mac_app_store_devil_in_the_details.html?lsrc=rss_main |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="appleinsider guidelines">{{cite web |url=http://www.appleinsider.com/articles/10/10/20/apple_issues_review_guidelines_for_mac_app_store.html |title=Apple issues review guidelines for Mac App Store |author=AppleInsider Staff |date=20 October 2010 |work=AppleInsider.com |publisher= |accessdate=24 October 2010 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205065320/https://appleinsider.com/articles/10/10/20/apple_issues_review_guidelines_for_mac_app_store.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>
<small>{{HideH|苹果禁止上架的应用程式种类}}
*改变原生使用者界面元素或行为的软件；
*不使用沙盒的應用程式。
