== 仿冒应用程序 ==
在独立游戏开发商[[Wolfire_Games|Wolfire Games]]将其游戏Lugaru HD以9.99美元的价格发布到Mac App Store后不久，开发商就注意到有一个仿冒他们的游戏以0.99美元的价格上架销售。开发商于2011年1月31日与苹果联系，2月10日，仿冒的游戏从Mac App Store中移除。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/32966/Apple_Pulls_Counterfeit_Lugaru_From_Mac_App_Store.php |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2012-01-20 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015149/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/32966/Apple_Pulls_Counterfeit_Lugaru_From_Mac_App_Store.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>

许多新闻网站认为，对已有应用程序的仿冒版本不应该能通过苹果的审核流程，且苹果对于开发者举报仿冒的反应时间很难接受。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.destructoid.com/lugaru-shamelessly-resold-without-consent-on-itunes-193156.phtml | title=Lugaru shamelessly resold without consent on iTunes | accessdate=2011-02-04 | author=Tan, Maurice | date=2011-02-03 | publisher=Destructoid | archive-date=2020-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925040206/https://www.destructoid.com/lugaru-shamelessly-resold-without-consent-on-itunes-193156.phtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 影响 ==
Mac App Store携超过1000个程序上线，包括[[iWork|iWork]]、[[iLife|iLife]]、[[Aperture|Aperture]]和移植自[[iOS|iOS]]的第三方应用程序[[Angry_Birds|Angry Birds]]、[[Flight_Control|Flight Control]]和[[Tweetie|Twitter]]。<ref name="1-6-10-PCMAG-MACAPPSTORE" /><ref name="1-6-10-BIZINSIDER-ANGRYBIRDS" /><ref name="1-6-10-TUAW-MAS1000" /><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://prmac.com/release-id-20275.htm |title=Gravilux: An iPad App Moves to the Desktop via the New Mac App Store, prMac, January 6, 2011 |accessdate=2012-01-20 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205065330/https://prmac.com/release-id-20275.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>最常见的定价在20到50美元区间内。<ref name="1-6-10-TUAW-MAS1000">{{cite web | url=http://www.tuaw.com/2011/01/06/mac-app-store-by-the-numbers-almost-1-000-apps-on-day-one/ | title=Mac App Store by the numbers -- almost 1,000 apps on Day One | accessdate=2011-01-06 | author=Gaywood, Richard | date=2011-01-06 | publisher=TUAW | archive-date=2015-01-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150131111626/http://www.tuaw.com/2011/01/06/mac-app-store-by-the-numbers-almost-1-000-apps-on-day-one/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> 在iOS [[App_Store|App Store]]受欢迎的游戏[[Angry_Birds|Angry Birds]]的Mac版本是Mac App Store上线首日排名第一的付费应用程序。<ref name="1-6-10-BIZINSIDER-ANGRYBIRDS">{{cite web | url=http://www.businessinsider.com/surprise-surprise-angry-birds-already-the-1-paid-mac-app-2011-1 | title=Surprise, Surprise: "Angry Birds" Already The #1 Paid Mac App | accessdate=2011-01-06 | author=Frommer, Dan | date=2011-01-06 | publisher=Silicon Alley Insider | archive-date=2020-07-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200728092559/https://www.businessinsider.com/surprise-surprise-angry-birds-already-the-1-paid-mac-app-2011-1 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 支付方式 ==
与[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]、iOS [[App_Store_(iOS)|App Store]]、[[iBookstore|iBookstore]]相同，用户在Mac App Store购买App时，商店会从其[[Apple_ID|Apple ID]]绑定的支付方式中扣款。不同地区商店支持的支付方式可能包括[[Visa|Visa]]、[[万事达|万事达]]、[[美国运通|美国运通]]、[[Discover|Discover]]信用卡、[[PayPal|PayPal]]、礼品卡等。不同地区商店使用的货币种类不同，主要包括[[美元|美元]]和[[欧元|欧元]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://support.apple.com/kb/HT2001 |title=App Store Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) |accessdate=2012-07-02 |date=2010-06-21 |publisher=Apple Inc. |archive-date=2014-07-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702140736/http://support.apple.com/kb/HT2001 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

